{"tid":1412482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於日後集會同示威嘅小建議","createTime":"2019-08-05T06:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:47:14.000Z","uid":167956,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0baa65db8f5718cc7acfb3340eb165a3fcbec5","tid":1412482,"uid":167956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"我地下次遊行同集會<br />\n不如每人都攞住維尼同毛主席嘅彩照<br />\n記住搵個相框鑲起佢<br />\n之後揮住國旗國徽<br />\n帶住毛語錄起身<br />\n有警察黎就話同朋友一齊研究毛語錄<br />\n警棍黎就用維尼同毛主席黎擋<br />\n呢啲畫面大陸一定出唔到街<br />\n如果打爆左毛主席<br />\n大陸宜家仲有大量撐毛份子<br />\n見到毛主席比黑警打爆一定會癲<br />\n然後我地要爆喊鬧啲黑警打爆左毛主席<br />\n好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠膽就拉9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}